name: src/module/plugin/syntax/AbstractSyntaxLoader.js
AbstractSyntaxLoader
description:
Provides the base implementation for all syntax loader plugins which automatically associates member methods
to syntax definitions invoking the method with escomplex settings and assigning the result to the same name as
the method.

name: onLoadSyntax
description: Loads all member methods including from child classes that are not `constructor` or `onConfigure`.

name: s_GET_ALL_PROPERTY_NAMES
description: Walks an objects inheritance tree collecting property names stopping before `AbstractSyntaxLoader` is reached.

name: src/module/report/AbstractReport.js
AbstractReport
description:
Provides several helper methods to work with method oriented data stored as `this.aggregate` in `ClassReport` /
`ModuleReport` and directly in `MethodReport`.

name: constructor
description:
If given assigns the method report to an internal variable. This is used by `ClassReport` and `ModuleReport`
which stores a `MethodReport` respectively in `this.aggregate`.

params.name: methodReport
params.description: A MethodReport to associate with this report.
params.descriptionRaw: A MethodReport to associate with this report.

name: _methodReport
description: Stores any associated `MethodReport`.

name: finalize
description: Cleans up any house keeping member variables.

name: methodReport
description:
Returns the associated `MethodReport` or `this`. Both ClassReport and ModuleReport have an `aggregate`
MethodReport.

name: incrementDistinctHalsteadItems
description: Increments the associated MethodReport Halstead for distinct names including aliasing any built-in property names.

name: incrementHalsteadItems
description: Increments the associated MethodReport Halstead items including distinct and total counts.

name: incrementHalsteadMetric
description: Increments the associated MethodReport Halstead metric type.

name: incrementParams
description: Increments the associated MethodReport parameter count.

name: isHalsteadMetricDistinct
description: Returns true if a given metric / identifier is not found in the associated MethodReport.

name: src/module/report/HalsteadData.js
HalsteadData
description: Provides all Halstead metric data / parameters.

name: constructor
description: Initializes the default Halstead data.

name: bugs
description: Measures an estimate for the number of potential errors.

name: difficulty
description: Measures the difficulty of the program to write or understand.

name: effort
description: Measures the maintenance effort of the program.

name: length
description: Defines the number of operands and operators.

name: time
description: Measures potential coding time.

name: vocabulary
description: Defines the unique number of operands and operators.

name: volume
description: Measures how much information a reader of the code potential has to absorb to understand its meaning.

name: operands
description:
In general an operand participates in actions associated with operators. A distinct and total count is provided
with all identifiers.

name: operators
description: In general an operator carries out an action. A distinct and total count is provided with all identifiers.

name: reset
description: Resets the state of all Halstead data metrics without removing any operand or operator data.

name: src/module/report/ModuleReport.js
ModuleReport
description: Provides the default report object which stores data pertaining to a single file / module being processed.

name: constructor
description: Initializes the report.

name: aggregate
description: Stores the aggregate MethodReport for the module.

name: classes
description: Stores all ClassReport data for the module.

name: dependencies
description: Stores all parsed dependencies.

name: maintainability
description: Stores the maintainability index for a report.

name: methods
description: Stores all module MethodReport data found outside of any ES6 classes.

name: _scopeStackClass
description: Stores the current class report scope stack.

name: _scopeStackMethod
description: Stores the current method report scope stack.

name: addDependencies
description: Potentially adds given dependencies for tracking.

name: createScope
description: Creates a report scope when a class or method is entered.

name: finalize
description: Cleans up any house keeping member variables.

name: getCurrentClassReport
description: Returns the current class report.

name: getCurrentMethodReport
description: Returns the current method report.

name: halsteadItemEncountered
description:
Increments the Halstead `metric` for the given `identifier` for the ModuleReport and any current class or method
report being tracked.

name: incrementCyclomatic
description: Increments the cyclomatic metric for the ModuleReport and any current class or method report being tracked.

name: incrementLogicalSloc
description:
Increments the logical SLOC (source lines of code) metric for the ModuleReport and any current class or method
report being tracked.

name: popScope
description: Pops a report scope.

params.name: type
params.description: The report scope class or method to pop off the given stack.
params.descriptionRaw: The report scope `class` or `method` to pop off the given stack.

name: src/module/traits/Trait.js
Trait
description: Provides a wrapper around a data field which may be a function or other primitive value.

name: constructor
description: Initializes trait data.

name: type
description: Returns the typeof data being wrapper.

name: valueOf
description:
Returns the value of the given data. If the wrapped data is a function it is invoked with the given `params`
otherwise the data is returned directly.

params.name: params
params.description: Provides parameters which are forwarded onto any data stored as a function.
params.descriptionRaw: Provides parameters which are forwarded onto any data stored as a function.

name: src/module/traits/TraitHalstead.js
TraitHalstead
description:
Provides a wrapper around a data object hash which should contain an `identifier` field and potentially a `filter`
field.

name: constructor
description: Initializes the Halstead trait.

params.name: data
params.descriptionRaw: The data field to be wrapped.

name: filter
description:
Returns the value of the `filter` field of the wrapped data. If the wrapped `filter` field is a function it
is invoked with the given `params` otherwise the data is returned directly. If `filter` is not defined then
`true` is returned.

params.name: params
params.description: Provides parameters which are forwarded onto any data stored as a function.
params.descriptionRaw: Provides parameters which are forwarded onto any data stored as a function.

name: type
description: Returns the typeof data being wrapper.

name: valueOf
description:
